{"tid":1473412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第四次的民間記者會主題為：「 官警黑亂港禍經濟    」。","createTime":"2019-08-14T23:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:04:12.000Z","uid":73092,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f7b7842cec9cd3f238e7727ab8fc8653569646","tid":1473412,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:49:52.000Z","msg":"致各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n民間記者會傳媒邀請函<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n第四次的民間記者會主題為：「 官警黑亂港禍經濟    」。 團隊希望能借是次機會，提供多角度意見， 還原事實真 相    ，從而反駁警方及政府過去的謊言、以及社會的誤解和迷思。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年8月15日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間：14：00<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，由於會場座位有限，有興趣進場採訪的媒體請於 8月 14日（星期三）晚上12點30分或之前填妥附件資料，以電話（94377274）或電郵（pr640212@gmail.com ）覆示，以便安排。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n如有查詢，請聯絡金先生 （電話：94377274）。謝謝<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n<br />\n2019 年 8 月 14 日"},{"pid":"97aff651258240836f93414713011665cab97a10","tid":1473412,"uid":31110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:55:28.000Z","msg":"太多片要播<br />\n義士拉左個個都被私刑唉<br />\n<br />\n818。818"},{"pid":"5f1c17a5103855f98b11b6cf68273273146c8b5c","tid":1473412,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac00c4cc58c807446cb085faa85bfe497ae8dbd","tid":1473412,"uid":103353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"830200ff14adc6a2696cfb77b683b875223df19c","tid":1473412,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:16:22.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"367e798d9e2ec1c2bf7d3a8c2156e32dac2b3f3c","tid":1473412,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:16:36.000Z","msg":"幫手推啦